      We do everything we can in order to draw attention to you: You get the
      largest amount of space, displayed most often and a personal visit from
      one of the team. There are 4 spots available.
    %li
      %strong Gold:
      Similar to Platinum but with about half the amount of the space, and you
      are  displayed alongside a second Gold sponsor. There are 8 spots
      available.
    %li
      %strong Silver:
      As with the other plans, we will also drive as much attention to you as possible.
      However, we will only display a limited number of banners and links at once in
      most places. The number of silver sponsors is unlimited.
  %p
    All of these packages will run as long as the Travis CI crowd funding campaign lasts, but at least 6 months.
